      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FLY (3) has been airborne since his return to the races, winning impressively fresh and backing it up with a 1.3L victory over 1200m last time out. This shapes similarly and although he meets his rivals a touch worse at the weights, he looks as though he still has more to come. Looks primed to bring up the hat-trick. BRUNO BRUNO (2) was doing the chasing from a mile back behind FLY last timeout, ending up 1.3L away. The smaller field this time should play into his hands and he did lead over this track and trip two back. Meets FLY better at the weights and it wouldn't surprise to see him turn the tables. PLEASING SMILE (6) missed as the race favourite here last time out when 4.5L off the winner. Still a maiden but has some upside and won't be far away. VANGUARD LEGEND (1) will appreciate this trip on the fresh side and he can be in the finish. BOLLON (4) is worth including.",
